# Security Incident Response

- [ ] **Identify Scope of Breach** <!-- id: 0 -->
    - [ ] Determine which account was compromised (Wallet, GitHub, Email, etc.)
    - [ ] Assess if local machine access was gained
- [ ] **Immediate Containment** <!-- id: 1 -->
    - [ ] Rotate secrets found in `.env` (Private Keys, API Keys)
    - [ ] Ensure `.env` is in `.gitignore`
- [ ] **Codebase Security Audit** <!-- id: 2 -->
    - [ ] Scan for hardcoded secrets in source files
    - [ ] Review recent file modifications for suspicious code/backdoors
- [ ] **Verification** <!-- id: 3 -->
    - [ ] Confirm all secrets are rotated
    - [ ] Verify clean git status
